import React from 'react';
import {
    ContactMeWrapper,
    MediaWrapper,
    MediaLink,
    MediaName
} from "./ContactMeElements"

const ContactMeForm = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <>
                <ContactMeWrapper>
                    <MediaWrapper>
                        <MediaName>Email</MediaName>
                        <MediaLink>crosenberg8@gatech.edu</MediaLink>
                    </MediaWrapper>
                    <MediaWrapper>
                        <MediaName>LinkedIn</MediaName>
                        <MediaLink>https://www.linkedin.com/in/connorrosenberg/</MediaLink>
                    </MediaWrapper>
                    <MediaWrapper>
                        <MediaName>Instagram</MediaName>
                        <MediaLink>crosenberg8@gatech.edu</MediaLink>
                    </MediaWrapper>
                </ContactMeWrapper>
            </>
        </>
    )
}

export default ContactMeForm;
